WEBVTT

00:02.702 --> 00:04.838
- ♪ TIMMY IS AN AVERAGE KID ♪

00:04.904 --> 00:07.707
♪ THAT NO ONE UNDERSTANDS ♪

00:07.774 --> 00:09.809
♪ MOM AND DAD AND VICKY ♪

00:09.876 --> 00:11.311
♪ ALWAYS GIVING HIM COMMANDS ♪

00:11.378 --> 00:12.612
- BED TWERP!

00:12.679 --> 00:14.814
- ♪ THE DOOM AND GLOOM
UP IN HIS ROOM ♪

00:14.881 --> 00:17.317
♪ IS BROKEN INSTANTLY ♪

00:17.384 --> 00:19.986
♪ BY HIS MAGIC LITTLE FISH
WHO'LL GRANT HIS EVERY WISH ♪

00:20.053 --> 00:21.488
♪ 'CAUSE IN REALITY ♪

00:21.554 --> 00:24.924
♪ THEY ARE HIS ODD PARENTS,
FAIRLY ODD PARENTS ♪

00:24.991 --> 00:27.494
- WANDS AND WINGS.
- FLOATY CROWNY THINGS.

00:27.560 --> 00:29.662
- ♪ ODD PARENTS,
FAIRLY ODD PARENTS ♪

00:29.729 --> 00:32.399
♪ REALLY ROD, PEA POD
BUFF BOD, HOT ROD ♪

00:32.465 --> 00:34.868
- OBTUSE, RUBBER GOOSE,
GREEN MOOSE, GUAVA JUICE!

00:34.934 --> 00:38.104
GIANT SNAKE, BIRTHDAY CAKE,
LARGE FRIES AND CHOCOLATE SHAKE!

00:38.171 --> 00:40.573
- ♪ ODD PARENTS,
FAIRLY ODD PARENTS ♪

00:40.640 --> 00:43.009
♪ IT FLIPS YOUR LID
WHEN YOU ARE A KID ♪

00:43.076 --> 00:44.778
♪ WITH FAIRLY ODD PARENTS ♪

00:44.844 --> 00:45.779
- YEAH, RIGHT!

01:01.628 --> 01:03.263
- HONEY, THE TOILET'S BROKEN!

01:03.329 --> 01:04.431
- I'LL FIX IT!

01:04.497 --> 01:05.632
[clattering]

01:05.698 --> 01:07.100
- AAH!

01:07.167 --> 01:09.035
THANK YOU!

01:12.772 --> 01:14.607
- MY DESK IS KINDA WOBBLY.

01:14.674 --> 01:15.942
- I'LL FIX IT!

01:17.043 --> 01:18.445
[clattering]

01:18.511 --> 01:19.746
- AAH!

01:19.813 --> 01:21.147
THANK YOU!

01:21.214 --> 01:22.715
AW, MAN!

01:22.782 --> 01:24.150
THE TV'S BROKEN.

01:24.217 --> 01:26.786
- OH, WHATEVER YOU DO,
DON'T TELL YOUR FATHER.

01:26.853 --> 01:28.254
- I'LL FIX IT!

01:32.091 --> 01:33.259
- AAH!

01:33.326 --> 01:35.261
- I MADE THE TV
SQUIRT WATER!

01:35.328 --> 01:37.730
IT'S NOT SUPPOSED TO DO THAT.
IS IT?

01:37.797 --> 01:40.033
- NO...
BUT ON THE BRIGHT SIDE,

01:40.099 --> 01:42.535
THE TOILET NOW GETS
200 CHANNELS!

01:42.602 --> 01:44.237
- I'M A COMPLETE FAILURE.

01:44.304 --> 01:46.539
YESTERDAY, I TRIED TO FIX
A PENCIL SHARPENER AT WORK,

01:46.606 --> 01:49.309
AND THEY HAD TO
CALL IN THE COAST GUARD!

01:49.375 --> 01:51.411
- COME ON, DAD.
YOU'RE EXAGGERATING.

01:51.478 --> 01:53.213
- TELL THAT TO MITCH
FROM ACCOUNTING.

01:53.279 --> 01:55.648
HE CLUNG TO A FLOATING COPIER
FOR FOUR HOURS

01:55.715 --> 01:57.217
UNTIL THEY FISHED HIM OUT!

01:57.283 --> 01:59.285
OH...MITCH!

01:59.352 --> 02:03.022
- OH, HONEY, DON'T BE
SO HARD ON YOURSELF.

02:03.089 --> 02:06.326
WHAT DO YOU SAY WE MAKE SOME
POPCORN AND WATCH THE TOILET?

02:06.392 --> 02:09.596
- IT'S NO USE.
I'M AN INCOMPETENT BOOB!

02:09.662 --> 02:12.432
I'M JUST GONNA GO STAND
IN A GARBAGE CAN IN THE ALLEY

02:12.499 --> 02:14.100
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE!

02:14.167 --> 02:15.134
AAH!

02:15.201 --> 02:16.436
OH, COME ON!

02:16.503 --> 02:18.404
ALL I DID WAS OPEN THE DOOR!

02:19.839 --> 02:21.007
- COME ON, DAD.

02:21.074 --> 02:22.809
YOU CAN'T JUST STAND
IN A TRASH CAN

02:22.876 --> 02:24.210
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE.

02:24.277 --> 02:25.845
- NO, I KNOW, SON.

02:25.912 --> 02:29.449
THAT'S WHY I'M INSTALLING
THIS COMFY TRASH CAN BENCH.

02:29.516 --> 02:32.352
EEE. I CAN'T IMAGINE
THEY SELL MANY OF THESE.

02:32.418 --> 02:34.053
- DAD, MOM AND I NEED YOU.

02:34.120 --> 02:36.422
YOU'RE THE GLUE THAT HOLDS
OUR FAMILY TOGETHER.

02:36.489 --> 02:38.758
- WELL, IT BETTER BE
WATERPROOF GLUE.

02:38.825 --> 02:41.895
NOW, IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME,
I HAVE A BENCH TO INSTALL.

02:41.961 --> 02:44.831
LET'S SEE--"INSERT FLANGE "A"
INTO BENCH BRACKET "B."

02:44.898 --> 02:46.733
- AAH!

02:46.799 --> 02:49.068
- OH, I DON'T DESERVE
A BENCH!

02:49.135 --> 02:50.537
IRONICALLY,
IF I WANT TO THROW IT OUT,

02:50.603 --> 02:52.639
I HAVE TO LEAVE IT
WHERE IT IS.

02:52.705 --> 02:53.773
MY HEAD HURTS!

02:53.840 --> 02:57.143
- MAN, I REALLY FEEL BAD
FOR MY DAD.

02:57.210 --> 02:59.445
- YOU SHOULD FEEL BAD
FOR MITCH FROM ACCOUNTING.

02:59.512 --> 03:00.780
[humming]

03:00.847 --> 03:02.582
HE SHRIVELED UP LIKE A PRUNE

03:02.649 --> 03:05.118
IN THE GREAT
PENCIL SHARPENER FLOOD.

03:05.184 --> 03:06.452
- I MEAN, I LOVE THE GUY,

03:06.519 --> 03:08.187
BUT HE IS KIND OF A DISASTER.

03:08.254 --> 03:10.056
IT'S A GOOD THING
THERE'S ONLY ONE OF HIM!

03:10.123 --> 03:12.191
- TIMMY, TIMMY, TIMMY.

03:12.258 --> 03:13.893
WAIT! I LOST MY TRAIN OF
THOUGHT.

03:13.960 --> 03:16.162
- I THINK YOU WERE ABOUT
TO REMIND TIMMY

03:16.229 --> 03:18.531
THERE ISN'T ONLY ONE
OF HIS DAD.

03:18.598 --> 03:22.001
HE WISHED UP A WHOLE PLANET
OF THEM--REMEMBER?

03:22.068 --> 03:23.903
- NO, THAT WASN'T IT.
IT WAS SOMETHING ABOUT

03:23.970 --> 03:26.639
THE RADIOACTIVE URANIUM
I LEFT IN HIS CLOSET.

03:29.175 --> 03:30.810
- [growling]

03:30.877 --> 03:33.546
[roaring]

03:33.613 --> 03:35.615
- BY THE WAY,
I THINK YOU HAVE TERMITES.

03:35.682 --> 03:36.883
- WAIT! WANDA'S RIGHT.

03:36.950 --> 03:38.985
I DID WISH FOR A PLANET OF DADS.

03:39.052 --> 03:41.154
I WONDER HOW
THEY'RE ALL DOING NOW.

03:41.220 --> 03:44.157
[cheerful music]

03:44.223 --> 03:47.961
♪ ♪

03:48.027 --> 03:49.028
- EEE...

03:50.363 --> 03:51.864
- MORNING, DAD!

03:51.931 --> 03:53.666
- MORNING TO YOU, TOO, DAD.

03:53.733 --> 03:56.035
DID YOU WATCH <i> DANCING</i>
<i>WITH THE DADS</i> LAST NIGHT?

03:56.102 --> 03:58.705
- YEAH. WHO KNEW DAD
WOULD MAKE THE FINALS?

03:58.771 --> 04:00.239
- AND NOW FOR SPORTS.

04:00.306 --> 04:01.908
THE DADS BEAT THE DADS TODAY

04:01.975 --> 04:04.310
IN A ROUSING GAME OF DADBALL
AT DAD STADIUM.

04:04.377 --> 04:06.879
LOOKS LIKE TRADING DAD FOR DAD
REALLY PAID OFF!

04:06.946 --> 04:08.381
OOH! THIS JUST IN.

04:08.448 --> 04:10.583
PRESIDENT DAD IS ABOUT
TO ADDRESS THE PLANET.

04:10.650 --> 04:13.686
WE NOW GO LIVE
TO THE DAD HOUSE.

04:13.753 --> 04:15.121
[presidential-like music]

04:15.188 --> 04:16.755
- MY FELLOW DADS,

04:16.822 --> 04:19.058
EVER SINCE WE ABOLISHED
THE MONKEY WRENCH,

04:19.125 --> 04:21.694
WE'VE EVOLVED INTO A NEARLY
PERFECT CIVILIZATION.

04:21.761 --> 04:23.229
BUT AS YOU KNOW,

04:23.296 --> 04:25.632
WE'RE STILL MISSING SOMETHING
CRUCIAL IN OUR LIVES.

04:25.698 --> 04:28.368
AS I GAZE OUT THE WINDOW
AT OUR GREAT MOM-UMENTS

04:28.434 --> 04:30.870
OR STARE AT MY PRICELESS
<i>MOM-A-LISA,</i>

04:30.937 --> 04:33.072
OR EAT A DELICIOUS
MOM-LETTE...

04:33.139 --> 04:36.876
I STILL HAVE NO IDEA WHAT
THAT CRUCIAL MISSING PIECE IS!

04:36.943 --> 04:38.578
- MR. PRESIDENT!

04:38.645 --> 04:40.580
I'VE LOCATED THE THING
THAT'S MISSING IN OUR LIVES.

04:40.647 --> 04:42.048
- IS IT MOM-HATTEN
CLAM CHOWDER?

04:42.115 --> 04:43.616
'CAUSE I'M SICK
OF EATING MOM-LETTES.

04:43.683 --> 04:45.952
- NO, SIR.
IT'S A CREATURE NAMED MOM

04:46.019 --> 04:47.487
ON A PLANET CALLED EARTH.

04:47.553 --> 04:49.789
- OOH! NOTIFY THE SPACE FLEET.

04:49.856 --> 04:53.493
WE ARE GOING TO EARTH
TO GET THIS MOM THING.

04:53.559 --> 04:56.996
AND TO GET ME SOME MILK
TO WASH DOWN THESE MOM-AROONS.

04:57.063 --> 04:58.164
[loud chewing]

04:58.231 --> 04:59.732
GGAAAHHH!

05:03.436 --> 05:05.171
- MONKEY...WRENCH.

05:05.238 --> 05:06.906
[snoring]
WATER RISING.

05:06.973 --> 05:09.075
HANG ON, MITCH!

05:10.476 --> 05:12.111
- WHOA! WHAT'S GOING ON?

05:12.178 --> 05:14.080
- WELL,
WANDA BURNED THE BACON,

05:14.147 --> 05:15.515
AND I HAD A NIGHTMARE
THAT I WAS SMART

05:15.581 --> 05:17.784
AND PEOPLE HELD ME ACCOUNTABLE
FOR MY ACTIONS!

05:17.850 --> 05:19.018
OH, AND YEAH.

05:19.085 --> 05:20.453
THERE'S A FLEET
OF ALIEN SPACESHIPS

05:20.520 --> 05:21.654
HOVERING OVER THE HOUSE.

05:21.721 --> 05:23.222
SO WHAT'S GOING ON WITH YOU?

05:23.289 --> 05:24.991
- ALIEN SPACESHIPS!

05:25.058 --> 05:26.225
AAH!

05:28.728 --> 05:30.463
- GREETINGS, EARTHLINGS.

05:30.530 --> 05:31.964
OH, HI, TIMMY!

05:32.031 --> 05:33.299
all: HI, TIMMY!

05:33.366 --> 05:34.967
- WHOA! THOSE ARE THE DADS
I WISHED UP,

05:35.034 --> 05:37.704
AND THEY'VE EVOLVED
INTO AN ADVANCED CIVILIZATION.

05:37.770 --> 05:39.405
- NOT THAT ADVANCED.

05:39.472 --> 05:42.775
THEIR LEADER'S EATING A TACO
UPSIDE DOWN.

05:42.842 --> 05:44.544
- ANOTHER EMPTY TACO?

05:44.610 --> 05:46.112
HA! WHAT ARE THE ODDS?

05:46.179 --> 05:49.315
- UH, HI, DADS.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

05:49.382 --> 05:51.984
- WE'VE COME FOR THE CREATURE
YOU CALL MOM.

05:52.051 --> 05:54.120
- NO. YOU HAVE
A PERFECT CIVILIZATION.

05:54.187 --> 05:56.189
WHY WOULD YOU WANT TO ADD
A WOMAN TO IT?

05:56.255 --> 05:59.225
I'M NOT SMART, WANDA.
YOU CAN'T HOLD ME ACCOUNTABLE.

05:59.292 --> 06:00.626
- WAIT. WHAT DID YOU SAY?

06:00.693 --> 06:02.161
- EH...MY TACO'S EMPTY?

06:02.228 --> 06:03.896
- AFTER THAT.
- WHAT ARE THE ODDS?

06:03.963 --> 06:06.099
- AFTER THAT.
WHAT DID YOU SAY ABOUT MOM?

06:06.165 --> 06:08.568
- OH! EH...WE'VE COME FOR HER.

06:08.634 --> 06:10.636
- WHAT?
I CAN'T HAVE MY MOM!

06:10.703 --> 06:12.605
- [chuckling]
TIMMY, TIMMY, TIMMY.

06:12.672 --> 06:14.507
WAIT.
I LOST MY TRAIN OF THOUGHT.

06:14.574 --> 06:16.008
OH, RIGHT.

06:16.075 --> 06:17.977
WE'RE TAKING YOUR MOM
WHETHER YOU LIKE IT OR NOT!

06:18.044 --> 06:20.546
OUR MANLY PLANET
NEEDS HER.

06:20.613 --> 06:21.814
- WELL, SO DO I!

06:21.881 --> 06:24.016
I DON'T KNOW WHAT I'D DO
WITHOUT MY MOM.

06:26.018 --> 06:28.087
- TIMMY, DO YOUR HOMEWORK!

06:28.154 --> 06:29.689
[electronic game sounds]

06:29.756 --> 06:32.358
TIMMY, DO YOUR CHORES!

06:32.425 --> 06:34.393
TIMMY, DO YOUR TAXES!

06:34.460 --> 06:35.995
- I'M TEN!

06:36.062 --> 06:37.363
COME TO THINK OF IT,

06:37.430 --> 06:39.699
I WOULDN'T HAVE TO DO
ANYTHING WITHOUT MY MOM.

06:39.766 --> 06:40.867
YOU CAN TAKE HER.

06:40.933 --> 06:42.568
NO, WAIT!
YOU CAN'T HAVE HER.

06:42.635 --> 06:44.137
I LOVE HER,
AND I'D MISS HER.

06:44.203 --> 06:45.905
- YOU'RE YOUNG.
YOU'LL GET OVER IT.

06:45.972 --> 06:48.808
COMMENCING MOM EXTRACTION...

06:51.978 --> 06:54.981
- GUYS, WE CAN'T LET THE DADS
TAKE MY MOM.

06:55.047 --> 06:56.849
- AH! HOW ABOUT WE GIVE THEM
SOMEONE ELSE'S MOM?

06:56.916 --> 06:58.751
I KNOW,
WE'LL GIVE THEM WANDA.

06:58.818 --> 07:00.153
THEN THEY'LL BE SORRY.

07:00.219 --> 07:02.088
AND I WON'T HAVE TO
DO MY TAXES!

07:02.155 --> 07:04.857
- COSMO, THAT'S A GREAT IDEA.
- TIMMY!

07:04.924 --> 07:06.692
- I'M NOT GONNA
GIVE THEM <i> YOU,</i> WANDA.

07:06.759 --> 07:08.528
I HAVE ANOTHER MOM IN MIND.

07:08.594 --> 07:10.329
MR. CROCKER,
HOW'D YOU LIKE TO SEND

07:10.396 --> 07:12.498
YOUR MOTHER
ON A LITTLE VACATION?

07:12.565 --> 07:14.066
- I'M HERE, TURNER!

07:14.133 --> 07:15.635
POINT ME TO THE INCINERATOR!

07:15.701 --> 07:17.737
- DENZEL,
DO I GET MY SURPRISE NOW?

07:17.804 --> 07:19.839
- SOON, MOTHER.
SOON.

07:19.906 --> 07:22.642
- NOT SO FAST.
IF I DO THIS FOR YOU,

07:22.708 --> 07:24.076
I WANT AN "A".

07:24.143 --> 07:25.912
- I'LL GIVE YOU A "C".
- DEAL!

07:25.978 --> 07:27.046
NOW JUST GO UP FRONT

07:27.113 --> 07:28.714
AND LAY YOUR MOM GENTLY
ON THE LAWN.

07:30.850 --> 07:33.119
- OOH!
ARE WE AT THE HOTEL?

07:33.186 --> 07:35.855
- MY MOM'S IN THE SACK.
COME AND GET HER!

07:42.428 --> 07:43.863
- AAH!

07:43.930 --> 07:45.498
YOU GET AN "F", TURNER!

07:46.699 --> 07:48.467
- TIMMY, THAT WASN'T
YOUR MOM.

07:48.534 --> 07:50.203
WE'RE NOT EVEN SURE
IT WAS A WOMAN.

07:50.269 --> 07:52.738
WE'RE TAKING YOUR MOM,
AND YOU CAN'T STOP US.

07:52.805 --> 07:54.740
- GUYS, WE GOTTA
PROTECT MY MOM!

07:54.807 --> 07:58.110
NO TELLING WHAT DIABOLICAL TRAP
THEY'LL SET TO TAKE HER AWAY.

07:58.177 --> 07:59.645
- OH, MY!

07:59.712 --> 08:03.549
A TRAIL OF FLUFFY KITTENS
LEADING TO AN OMINOUS SHADOW.

08:03.616 --> 08:05.451
THAT'S NOT SUSPICIOUS AT ALL.

08:05.518 --> 08:07.720
I'LL CALL YOU SNOWBALL

08:07.787 --> 08:09.722
AND I'LL CALL YOU SNOWBALL,

08:09.789 --> 08:12.091
AND SINCE YOU'RE WHITE
AND FLUFFY,

08:12.158 --> 08:14.293
I'LL CALL YOU BOB.

08:16.696 --> 08:18.397
- WHERE'S COSMO?

08:18.464 --> 08:19.699
- HI, TIMMY!

08:19.765 --> 08:21.801
- AAH! I WISH MY MOM AND COSMO

08:21.868 --> 08:24.537
WERE SAFE INSIDE THE HOUSE!

08:27.039 --> 08:27.974
WHEW!

08:28.040 --> 08:29.342
- SHE JUST DISAPPEARED.

08:29.408 --> 08:30.643
HOW IS THAT POSSIBLE?

08:30.710 --> 08:32.645
- AS YOU RECALL,
YOUR PRESIDENTNESS,

08:32.712 --> 08:33.913
TIMMY HAS FAIRIES.

08:33.980 --> 08:35.648
HE USED THEIR MAGIC
TO CREATE US,

08:35.715 --> 08:38.551
AND NOW HE'S USING THEIR MAGIC
TO KEEP MOM TO HIMSELF.

08:38.618 --> 08:39.986
- WE'RE HANDSOME!

08:40.052 --> 08:41.386
- FOCUS, MR. PRESIDENT.

08:41.453 --> 08:43.823
I HAVE A PLAN
TO DRAIN THE FAIRIES' MAGIC.

08:43.890 --> 08:45.791
- OOH! HOW ARE WE
GONNA DO THAT?

08:45.858 --> 08:48.527
- WE'RE NOT GOING TO DO THAT.
TIMMY IS!

08:48.594 --> 08:49.528
[beep]

08:57.069 --> 08:59.171
WHOOPS! OH, MY AIM
WAS REALLY OFF THERE.

08:59.238 --> 09:01.674
LUCKILY,
I BUILT TWO ROBOTS.

09:06.646 --> 09:08.281
- THANKS FOR SAVING
MY MOM, GUYS.

09:08.347 --> 09:11.651
I BETTER GO KEEP AN EYE ON HER
UNTIL THAT SPACESHIP LEAVES.

09:11.717 --> 09:13.185
HI, GUYS.
- DID YOU FORGET SOMETHING,

09:13.252 --> 09:14.587
SPORT?
- YEAH.

09:14.654 --> 09:16.789
I FORGOT TO MAKE
10,000 WISHES.

09:19.525 --> 09:21.360
- MOM,
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

09:21.427 --> 09:23.062
- WELL...

09:23.129 --> 09:25.932
APPARENTLY,
I'M ALLERGIC TO KITTENS.

09:25.998 --> 09:27.867
AH-CHOO!

09:27.934 --> 09:29.402
- AND I WISH FOR A PONY
AND A RACECAR AND A JUKEBOX

09:29.468 --> 09:31.003
AND A PING-PONG TABLE AND A
ROLLERCOASTER AND A SKATEBOARD--

09:31.070 --> 09:32.271
- MOM, YOU CAN'T LEAVE
THE HOUSE--

09:32.338 --> 09:33.572
THE DADS'LL GET YOU.

09:33.639 --> 09:35.274
I MEAN,
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

09:35.341 --> 09:37.977
- TO THE STORE FOR CAT FOOD
AND ANTIHISTAMINES.

09:42.348 --> 09:44.984
[tires squealing]

09:46.085 --> 09:47.753
- MOM, NO!

09:47.820 --> 09:51.357
- BYE, TIMMY.
I'M OFF TO THE STORE.

09:51.424 --> 09:55.661
[dramatic music]

09:55.728 --> 09:57.830
- AAH! COSMO, WANDA!

09:57.897 --> 10:00.399
- AND A GUMBALL MACHINE
AND A MAGNIFYING GLASS AND A--

10:00.466 --> 10:02.401
- TIMMY, YOUR ROOM IS TOTALLY
FULL OF WISHES.

10:02.468 --> 10:05.671
THERE'S BARELY ROOM FOR US,
LET ALONE WANDA'S GIANT EGO.

10:05.738 --> 10:07.506
- I DON'T HAVE A GIANT EGO!

10:07.573 --> 10:10.242
- REALLY? THEN HOW DO YOU
EXPLAIN THIS COFFEE MUG

10:10.309 --> 10:12.912
THAT SAYS, "WANDA IS AWESOME"?

10:12.979 --> 10:14.347
WE DON'T HAVE ROOM FOR THIS!
[crash]

10:14.413 --> 10:15.848
- YOU WANNA SAVE ROOM IN HERE?

10:15.915 --> 10:17.750
THEN YOU BE
THE MAGNIFYING GLASS.

10:22.321 --> 10:23.723
- SPORT...

10:23.789 --> 10:25.725
I'M REALLY HOT.

10:25.791 --> 10:28.094
- THERE IT IS,
THAT GIANT EGO AGAIN.

10:28.160 --> 10:30.830
- YOU WANNA COOL OFF?
I WISH YOU WERE A BLOCK OF ICE.

10:33.499 --> 10:35.701
- TIMMY,
YOU'RE SQUISHING POOF.

10:35.768 --> 10:37.570
- WELL, MAYBE IT WOULD HELP
IF YOU WERE SMALLER.

10:37.636 --> 10:38.871
I WISH POOF WAS A BUG.

10:41.674 --> 10:44.143
- OKAY, SPORT,
ENOUGH'S ENOUGH.

10:44.210 --> 10:45.644
WISH US BACK TO NORMAL.

10:45.711 --> 10:47.513
- MISSION ACCOMPLISHED.

10:47.580 --> 10:49.515
YOUR MAGIC HAS BEEN DRAINED.

10:49.582 --> 10:51.684
INITIATING SELF-DESTRUCT.

10:51.751 --> 10:55.021
[rapid beeping]

10:56.455 --> 10:58.657
- OH, NO, TIMMY EXPLODED!

10:58.724 --> 11:00.393
WE ARE SO FIRED!

11:00.459 --> 11:01.660
- GUYS, YOU GOTTA HELP ME!

11:01.727 --> 11:03.529
AAH!
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

11:03.596 --> 11:04.864
- NOT NOW, TIMMY.

11:04.930 --> 11:07.366
WE'RE TOO SAD
ABOUT TIMMY BLOWING UP.

11:07.433 --> 11:10.069
- WAIT A MINUTE!
THAT WASN'T THE REAL TIMMY.

11:10.136 --> 11:11.637
WE'VE BEEN TRICKED.

11:11.704 --> 11:13.873
- OKAY. I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT,

11:13.939 --> 11:15.408
BUT THE DADS GOT MY MOM!

11:15.474 --> 11:17.109
YOU'VE GOTTA POOF HER
OFF THE SHIP!

11:17.176 --> 11:18.110
<i>[Call to Post]</i>

11:18.177 --> 11:19.478
[pfft]
- OH, NO!

11:19.545 --> 11:20.980
WE'RE OUT OF MAGIC!

11:21.047 --> 11:22.681
- AAH! WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

11:22.748 --> 11:24.550
- THINGS DO NOT LOOK GOOD.

11:24.617 --> 11:26.852
BUT THAT COULD BE BECAUSE
I'M STANDING UNDER A PONY.

11:26.919 --> 11:29.588
EASY, BUTTERSCOTCH!

11:35.461 --> 11:37.563
- [snoring]
EH...LOOK OUT, MITCH.

11:37.630 --> 11:39.965
SHARKS...CIRCLING THE COPIER!

11:40.032 --> 11:41.767
- I'VE GOTTA SAVE MY MOM!

11:41.834 --> 11:44.003
HOW LONG BEFORE YOU GUYS
GET YOUR MAGIC BACK?

11:44.070 --> 11:45.905
- OUR WANDS
HAVE TO RECHARGE.

11:45.971 --> 11:47.239
IT'LL TAKE HOURS

11:47.306 --> 11:49.475
WHILE THE MAGIC DOWNLOADS
FROM FAIRY WORLD.

11:49.542 --> 11:50.810
- OH, GREAT.

11:50.876 --> 11:53.212
HOW AM I GONNA GET
TO THE PLANET OF THE DADS?

11:53.279 --> 11:56.082
- IF ONLY YOU'D WISHED UP
A SPACESHIP BEFORE YOU EXPLODED.

11:56.148 --> 11:57.583
OOH, LOOK!
A GIANT QUARTER.

11:57.650 --> 11:58.851
WE'RE RICH!

11:58.918 --> 12:00.920
WE CAN BUY A SPACESHIP NOW.

12:00.986 --> 12:02.788
- A SPACESHIP.
THAT'S IT.

12:02.855 --> 12:05.024
WE CAN BORROW MARK CHANG'S.

12:05.091 --> 12:07.793
- COSMO!
YOU'RE MAKING ME MELT.

12:07.860 --> 12:09.862
- THIS IS NO TIME
FOR ROMANCE, WANDA.

12:09.929 --> 12:12.832
TIMMY'S GOT A PROBLEM.

12:12.898 --> 12:16.202
- EVERYONE HOP ON THE PONY.
WE'RE GOING TO THE DUMP!

12:16.268 --> 12:18.737
- DON'T SAY DUMP
IN FRONT OF BUTTERSCOTCH!

12:19.772 --> 12:21.006
- ♪ OH, VICKY ♪

12:21.073 --> 12:23.375
♪ YOU ARE SO ICKY ♪

12:23.442 --> 12:25.277
♪ YOU ARE SO SICKY ♪

12:25.344 --> 12:26.712
♪ AND TICKY ♪

12:26.779 --> 12:28.147
♪ OH, VICKY ♪

12:28.214 --> 12:29.715
♪ OH, VICKY ♪

12:29.782 --> 12:31.717
- MARK, I NEED YOUR HELP.

12:31.784 --> 12:33.953
- YO, TIMMY!
LIKE DITTO!

12:34.019 --> 12:36.856
CAN YOU SCRUB MY BACK
WITH THE BOTTOM OF YOUR SHOE?

12:36.922 --> 12:38.224
- NOT NOW, MARK!

12:38.290 --> 12:39.892
A BUNCH OF ALIEN DADS
STOLE MY MOM

12:39.959 --> 12:42.027
AND TURNED MY FLOATY FRIENDS
INTO A MAGNIFYING GLASS,

12:42.094 --> 12:43.596
A BLOCK OF ICE, AND A BUG!

12:43.662 --> 12:45.331
- OH. BUSY MORNING.

12:45.397 --> 12:47.366
ALL I DID WAS TAKE OUT
THE CEREAL

12:47.433 --> 12:49.034
AND EAT A BOWL OF TRASH.

12:49.101 --> 12:51.003
[belch]

12:51.070 --> 12:53.205
- DON'T YOU MEAN
YOU TOOK OUT THE TRASH

12:53.272 --> 12:54.740
AND ATE A BOWL OF CEREAL?

12:54.807 --> 12:56.909
- EEW! THAT'S GROSS!

12:56.976 --> 13:00.045
TIMMY, YOUR BLOCK OF ICE
IS A SICKO.

13:01.514 --> 13:03.282
- YOU GOTTA FIRE UP
YOUR SHIP, MARK.

13:03.349 --> 13:04.884
THERE'S NO TELLING
WHAT TERRIBLE THINGS

13:04.950 --> 13:06.619
THOSE DADS ARE DOING
TO MY MOM.

13:06.685 --> 13:09.555
- OH, UP AND AWAY, DUDE!

13:10.956 --> 13:12.591
- YOU KNOW,
YOU PEOPLE REMIND ME

13:12.658 --> 13:15.628
OF A MUCH LESS WET VERSION
OF MY HUSBAND.

13:15.694 --> 13:17.463
- ALLOW ME TO EXPLAIN.

13:17.530 --> 13:18.964
WE'RE TAKING YOU
TO OUR PLANET

13:19.031 --> 13:20.699
TO WORSHIP YOU
AS OUR QUEEN!

13:20.766 --> 13:22.835
- OOH! THAT SOUNDS NICE.

13:22.902 --> 13:24.904
I JUST HAVE TO GET BACK
BY THURSDAY.

13:24.970 --> 13:26.939
I'VE GOTTA GET MY HUSBAND
OUT OF THE TRASH CAN

13:27.006 --> 13:28.374
BEFORE THE GARBAGE MEN COME.

13:32.278 --> 13:34.280
- OKAY. WE NEED A WAY
TO DISTRACT THE DADS

13:34.346 --> 13:35.781
SO WE CAN RESCUE MY MOM.

13:35.848 --> 13:37.216
- USE THIS, DUDE.

13:37.283 --> 13:41.754
IT WAS A VALENTINE PRE-SENT
FROM MY BELOVED VICKY.

13:41.820 --> 13:43.289
- CHOCOLATE-COVERED
CHERRY BOMBS.

13:43.355 --> 13:45.191
AWESOME!
WE'LL SET UP AN EXPLOSION

13:45.257 --> 13:46.458
AND SNEAK OFF WITH MY MOM.

13:46.525 --> 13:48.227
HEY, WHERE'S WANDA?

13:48.294 --> 13:49.328
- I PUT HER IN THE FREEZER

13:49.395 --> 13:51.463
TO KEEP HER FROM MELTING
ANY WORSE.

13:51.530 --> 13:53.365
LOOKING GOOD, HONEY.

13:53.432 --> 13:55.868
HOLY COW, SHE'S HIDEOUS!

13:55.935 --> 13:57.803
- I HEARD THAT!
- NOT YOU, SWEETIE.

13:57.870 --> 14:00.105
I WAS TALKING ABOUT...TIMMY.

14:00.172 --> 14:04.243
WOW! THE PLANET OF THE DADS
HAS THREE GIANT SUNS.

14:08.881 --> 14:11.717
YAY, CHOCOLATE!

14:11.784 --> 14:14.720
- all: MOM! MOM! MOM!

14:14.787 --> 14:16.622
MOM! MOM!

14:16.689 --> 14:19.925
- THIS IS THE SECOND NICEST
ALIEN PARADE IN MY HONOR

14:19.992 --> 14:21.794
I'VE EVER BEEN TO.

14:21.860 --> 14:23.629
- all: MOM! MOM! MOM!

14:27.433 --> 14:30.402
- WELCOME TO YOUR PALACE,
QUEEN MOM.

14:32.972 --> 14:34.873
- IT'S VERY NICE.

14:34.940 --> 14:36.875
BUT IT COULD USE
A WOMAN'S TOUCH.

14:38.244 --> 14:39.845
[all gasp]

14:39.912 --> 14:43.015
- YAY!
IT'S PERFECT.

14:43.082 --> 14:45.517
THE VOID IN OUR LIVES
HAS BEEN FILLED.

14:45.584 --> 14:48.854
MOM, WE'RE ALL GOING TO BE
SO HAPPY TOGETHER.

14:48.921 --> 14:50.389
WE'LL GO
TO FANCY RESTAURANTS,

14:50.456 --> 14:51.757
TAKE LONG WALKS
ON THE BEACH,

14:51.824 --> 14:53.592
AND YOU WILL MAKE
OUR FRIDAY NIGHT DANCES

14:53.659 --> 14:54.827
WAY LESS ICKY.

14:54.893 --> 14:57.329
- WELL, THAT SOUNDS FUN.

14:57.396 --> 14:59.064
BUT I-I NEED
TO GO HOME NOW.

14:59.131 --> 15:00.299
- HOME?

15:00.366 --> 15:02.401
I'M SORRY,
BUT YOU CAN'T LEAVE.

15:03.769 --> 15:04.870
THIS IS YOUR NEW HOME.

15:04.937 --> 15:06.772
FOREVER.
- SAY WHAT NOW?

15:06.839 --> 15:08.841
- YOU SEE,
IN EXACTLY ONE HOUR,

15:08.907 --> 15:10.943
THIS GIANT WORMHOLE
IS GOING TO OPEN.

15:11.010 --> 15:12.745
THEN WE'RE GOING TO FIRE
A THRUSTER

15:12.811 --> 15:14.813
THAT WILL SHOOT OUR PLANET
INSIDE.

15:14.880 --> 15:17.216
WE'LL DISAPPEAR
INTO A DISTANT GALAXY

15:17.283 --> 15:20.219
WHERE NO ONE CAN EVER
TAKE YOU AWAY FROM US.

15:20.286 --> 15:21.687
- YOU CAN'T DO THAT!

15:21.754 --> 15:23.289
MY FAMILY NEEDS ME.

15:23.355 --> 15:25.024
AND I NEED THEM.

15:25.090 --> 15:26.558
ALSO, I DIDN'T PACK

15:26.625 --> 15:28.260
FOR A TRIP
THROUGH A WORMHOLE.

15:31.563 --> 15:34.833
[shrieking]
HELP!

15:34.900 --> 15:37.069
- OH, NO!
WE'VE GOTTA DO SOMETHING.

15:37.136 --> 15:39.271
GUYS,
ARE YOUR WANDS RECHARGED?

15:39.338 --> 15:42.541
- UH, MINE'S ONLY
AT 50%, SPORT.

15:42.608 --> 15:44.143
- HOLD ON.
LET ME CHECK MINE.

15:44.209 --> 15:45.544
- [shrieks]
POOF POOF!

15:45.611 --> 15:46.945
[moans]

15:47.012 --> 15:48.280
- OOPS.
SORRY, POOF.

15:48.347 --> 15:50.015
- WAIT.
WE DON'T NEED MAGIC.

15:50.082 --> 15:51.383
MARK HAS A FAKE-A-FIER.

15:51.450 --> 15:52.785
QUICK, MARK.

15:52.851 --> 15:54.553
TURN INTO SOMETHING
THAT'LL STOP THE DADS.

15:54.620 --> 15:57.956
- NO PROBLEMO, BRAH!

15:58.023 --> 16:00.426
- THAT'S YOUR SECRET WEAPON?
BUTTER?

16:00.492 --> 16:01.627
- SHA!

16:01.694 --> 16:04.296
ALL THE DADS HAVE TO DO
IS EAT ME,

16:04.363 --> 16:08.167
AND THEIR CHOLESTEROL
WILL GO THROUGH THE ROOF.

16:08.233 --> 16:09.802
IN A MATTER OF MONTHS,

16:09.868 --> 16:13.539
THEY'LL BE OUT OF SHAPE
AND EASY TO OVERPOWER.

16:13.605 --> 16:14.807
- THAT WON'T WORK!

16:14.873 --> 16:16.608
WE NEED TO STOP THEM NOW.

16:18.744 --> 16:20.212
THAT'S MORE LIKE IT.

16:20.279 --> 16:22.481
- all: EEH!

16:22.548 --> 16:24.116
LOOK, IT'S TIMMY.

16:24.183 --> 16:25.484
HI, TIMMY!

16:25.551 --> 16:26.819
- ALL RIGHT, DADS.

16:26.885 --> 16:28.387
HAND OVER MY MOM!

16:28.454 --> 16:30.556
- SORRY,
BUT YOU CAN'T HAVE YOUR MOM.

16:30.622 --> 16:32.224
WE WENT THROUGH
A LOT OF TROUBLE

16:32.291 --> 16:34.293
AND KITTENS
TO GET HER.

16:34.360 --> 16:38.130
[dramatic music]

16:38.197 --> 16:40.132
- AAH!
THERE ARE TOO MANY OF THEM.

16:40.199 --> 16:41.800
WE DON'T STAND A CHANCE.

16:41.867 --> 16:43.068
- I KNOW.

16:43.135 --> 16:45.137
I CAN TURN MYSELF
INTO SOME LEAD PAINT.

16:45.204 --> 16:46.171
IF THEY LICK ME,

16:46.238 --> 16:47.840
IN, LIKE, 20 YEARS...

16:47.906 --> 16:48.974
- all: GET TIMMY.
GET TIMMY.

16:49.041 --> 16:50.342
- RETREAT!

16:55.681 --> 16:58.917
- UP, UP, AND AWAY AGAIN,
DUDE!

16:58.984 --> 17:00.586
- all: BYE, TIMMY.

17:01.720 --> 17:03.322
- GOTTA THINK!

17:03.389 --> 17:04.890
IN LESS THAN AN HOUR,
MY MOM WILL BE

17:04.957 --> 17:06.858
SHOT INTO A WORMHOLE
AND GONE FOREVER.

17:06.925 --> 17:08.660
HOW SOON TILL YOUR WANDS
HAVE POWER?

17:08.727 --> 17:11.163
- WE'RE ONLY AT 70%, SPORT.

17:11.230 --> 17:13.365
WE WON'T HAVE OUR MAGIC BACK
IN TIME.

17:13.432 --> 17:15.166
- THE HIDEOUS
MELTING ICE BLOB

17:15.233 --> 17:16.667
THAT USED TO BE WANDA
IS RIGHT.

17:16.734 --> 17:18.170
YOU'RE ON YOUR OWN,
TIMMY.

17:18.237 --> 17:20.204
- HOW'D THEY GET SO ADVANCED?

17:20.271 --> 17:21.673
I MEAN,
THEY'RE BASED ON MY DAD,

17:21.740 --> 17:23.509
AND HE'S
A WALKING DISASTER.

17:23.575 --> 17:24.675
- IT'S TRUE.

17:24.742 --> 17:26.444
HE DESTROYS EVERYTHING
HE TOUCHES.

17:26.512 --> 17:29.348
THE TOILET, THE TV,
YOUR CHILDHOOD.

17:29.415 --> 17:31.049
- WAIT A MINUTE.
MY DAD!

17:31.116 --> 17:32.851
HE MIGHT BE
EXACTLY WHAT WE NEED.

17:32.918 --> 17:34.019
- REALLY?

17:34.086 --> 17:36.255
'CAUSE I DO HAVE
SOME DYNAMITE.

17:36.321 --> 17:38.791
- OH, LOOK.
WE'RE PASSING THE SUNS AGAIN.

17:41.160 --> 17:43.729
I SHOULD REALLY STAY AWAY
FROM THE WINDOW.

17:48.967 --> 17:50.369
- AAH!

17:50.436 --> 17:51.937
DAD, WHAT HAPPENED?

17:52.004 --> 17:53.806
- I TRIED TO MAKE DINNER
FOR YOUR MOM

17:53.872 --> 17:55.874
TO APOLOGIZE
FOR FLOODING THE HOUSE,

17:55.941 --> 17:57.309
AND I FLOODED THE HOUSE!

17:57.376 --> 17:59.077
[sobbing]

17:59.144 --> 18:00.312
- GET IT TOGETHER, DAD!

18:00.379 --> 18:01.914
MOM'S BEEN KIDNAPPED
BY ALIENS,

18:01.980 --> 18:03.348
AND I NEED YOUR HELP
TO SAVE HER.

18:03.415 --> 18:06.485
- YOU'RE JUST TRYING
TO MAKE ME FEEL BETTER.

18:06.552 --> 18:07.853
FACE IT, SON,

18:07.920 --> 18:10.155
I DESTROY
EVERYTHING I TOUCH.

18:12.458 --> 18:14.259
- THAT'S WHAT I'M COUNTING ON.

18:14.326 --> 18:15.327
- [yells]

18:15.394 --> 18:17.262
I'M SPINNING!

18:23.569 --> 18:24.636
- WHOA.

18:24.703 --> 18:26.271
THIS IS GONNA BE HARDER
THAN I THOUGHT.

18:26.338 --> 18:28.006
MARK,
WE NEED A DISGUISE.

18:28.073 --> 18:29.641
- YOU GOT IT, BRO!

18:29.708 --> 18:31.543
NO.

18:31.610 --> 18:33.712
NO.

18:33.779 --> 18:34.746
WHOOPS.

18:34.813 --> 18:36.014
THAT'S THE "TURN THE SHIP

18:36.081 --> 18:38.517
INTO A CHINESE RESTAURANT"
BUTTON.

18:38.584 --> 18:39.885
- I SMELL EGG ROLLS.

18:42.955 --> 18:45.324
SPINNING AGAIN!

18:48.727 --> 18:50.729
WHAT A HANDSOME PLANET.

18:50.796 --> 18:52.331
NOW THE QUESTION IS,

18:52.397 --> 18:54.099
WHERE ARE THEY KEEPING
YOUR MOTHER?

18:54.166 --> 18:56.101
- UH, IN THE MOM-SHAPED
BUILDING.

18:56.168 --> 18:58.170
- BOY, THOSE ALIENS
ARE DUMB.

18:58.237 --> 19:01.340
YOUR REAL MOTHER DOESN'T HAVE
A DOOR IN HER CHIN.

19:01.406 --> 19:02.841
HOW ARE WE GONNA GET IN?

19:02.908 --> 19:05.777
THE PLACE IS GUARDED
BY AN ARMY OF MALE MODELS.

19:05.844 --> 19:06.945
- HERE'S THE PLAN.

19:07.012 --> 19:08.013
[whispering]

19:08.080 --> 19:09.281
[trumpet fanfare]

19:09.348 --> 19:12.818
- HEY, FELLOW
INTERGALACTIC DAD TYPES.

19:12.885 --> 19:13.986
I CAUGHT TIMMY!

19:14.052 --> 19:15.153
- all: HI, TIMMY!

19:15.220 --> 19:18.156
- LIVE LONG AND PROPANE.

19:24.029 --> 19:27.299
- WORMHOLE LAUNCH
IN T-MINUS THREE MINUTES.

19:27.366 --> 19:28.867
- OKAY.
I'M GONNA RESCUE MOM.

19:28.934 --> 19:30.102
YOU STOP THEM

19:30.168 --> 19:31.703
FROM LAUNCHING THE PLANET
INTO A WORMHOLE.

19:31.770 --> 19:32.804
- BUT HOW?

19:32.871 --> 19:33.906
- JUST TAKE YOUR WRENCH

19:33.972 --> 19:35.474
AND GO FIX
THAT CONTROL PANEL.

19:35.541 --> 19:38.110
- YEAH, I'M NOT SURE
I CAN DO THAT, TIMMY.

19:38.176 --> 19:39.611
FOR THE LOVE OF PETE,
I FLOODED THE HOUSE

19:39.678 --> 19:41.013
TRYING TO MAKE HOT DOGS!

19:41.079 --> 19:42.180
- HELP!

19:42.247 --> 19:43.749
GET ME OUT OF HERE!

19:43.815 --> 19:44.950
- THAT'S YOUR MOTHER.

19:45.017 --> 19:46.785
SHE SCREAMS THAT A LOT
IN HER SLEEP.

19:46.852 --> 19:47.819
ALL RIGHT, TIMMY.

19:47.886 --> 19:49.421
I'M GOING IN.

19:52.224 --> 19:54.059
[struggling]

19:54.126 --> 19:56.762
HELLO,
FELLOW ALIEN DAD TYPES.

19:56.828 --> 19:58.564
MAY THE HORSE BE WITH YOU.

19:58.630 --> 19:59.631
- [straining]

19:59.698 --> 20:00.933
THIS IS AN OUTRAGE.

20:00.999 --> 20:03.669
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
HOW TO TREAT A LADY,

20:03.735 --> 20:06.338
AND YOUR TOILET
GETS TERRIBLE RECEPTION.

20:06.405 --> 20:08.340
[static]

20:08.407 --> 20:10.509
- I'M GONNA NEED
SOME BACKUP.

20:12.344 --> 20:13.378
- all: HI, TIMMY!

20:13.445 --> 20:14.379
- UH-OH.

20:16.148 --> 20:17.382
- GOOD NEWS, SIR.

20:17.449 --> 20:19.618
WE CAUGHT TIMMY
TRYING TO RESCUE HIS MOM.

20:19.685 --> 20:22.321
- TIMMY!
YOU'VE COME TO SAVE ME.

20:22.387 --> 20:23.522
- WELL, I TRIED.

20:23.589 --> 20:25.490
NOW IT'S UP TO DAD
TO SAVE US BOTH.

20:25.557 --> 20:26.658
- HE'S HERE?

20:26.725 --> 20:28.427
YOU GOT HIM
OUT OF HIS TRASH CAN?

20:28.493 --> 20:30.062
- NO.
YOU DID, MOM.

20:30.128 --> 20:31.563
HE CAME TO RESCUE YOU.

20:31.630 --> 20:34.032
- THAT'S SO SWEET.

20:34.099 --> 20:36.368
BUT I'M SURPRISED
THE PLACE ISN'T FLOODED.

20:36.435 --> 20:38.770
- IF MY PLAN WORKS,
IT WILL BE.

20:43.175 --> 20:45.344
- EEH...UH-OH.

20:45.410 --> 20:47.879
THE DOOHICKEY
NEXT TO THIS THINGAMABOB

20:47.946 --> 20:49.014
IS ON THE FRITZ.

20:49.081 --> 20:50.749
BUT DON'T WORRY!
I'LL FIX IT.

20:50.816 --> 20:53.151
- NOT THE MONKEY WRENCH!
STOP HIM!

20:53.218 --> 20:56.288
[fighting]

20:56.355 --> 20:59.858
- WRENCH FIX!

21:01.660 --> 21:04.429
[triumphant music]

21:04.496 --> 21:11.670
♪ ♪

21:11.737 --> 21:12.971
I DID IT!

21:13.038 --> 21:15.073
I CLEVERLY DISGUISED MYSELF
AS ONE OF YOU

21:15.140 --> 21:17.843
AND THWARTED YOUR PLAN
WITHOUT BEING DISCOVERED.

21:17.909 --> 21:19.344
I STOPPED THE LAUNCH.

21:19.411 --> 21:21.847
I'M NOT A LOSER ANYMORE.

21:21.913 --> 21:25.017
- OH, I NEVER THOUGHT
YOU WERE A LOSER, HONEY.

21:25.083 --> 21:26.885
- I'M GONNA GIVE YOU
A BIG KISS,

21:26.952 --> 21:29.655
THEN TAKE YOU HOME
FOR SOME SOAKING WET HAMBURGERS.

21:29.721 --> 21:31.323
- [gibberish]

21:34.059 --> 21:36.028
- [both gasp]

21:36.094 --> 21:39.598
- AT LEAST I DIDN'T HAVE
TO WATCH THEM KISS.

21:39.665 --> 21:42.534
- NICE RESCUE, DUDE.

21:42.601 --> 21:45.137
NOW, WHERE DID I PARK
THE SHIP?

21:45.203 --> 21:46.338
[beep]
HEY!

21:46.405 --> 21:47.639
FOUND IT.

21:55.147 --> 21:56.415
- YOU DID IT, SPORT.

21:56.481 --> 21:57.816
YOU SAVED YOUR MOM.

21:57.883 --> 22:00.152
- GUYS, YOUR WANDS
ARE RECHARGED.

22:00.218 --> 22:02.421
- YEAH, LIKE 20 MINUTES AGO.

22:02.487 --> 22:03.889
DIDN'T YOU GET OUR TEXT?

22:03.955 --> 22:05.624
- LET'S JUST GET OUT OF HERE.

22:05.691 --> 22:08.460
[dads sobbing]

22:10.696 --> 22:12.364
- THEY MISS HER, SPORT.

22:12.431 --> 22:14.433
YOU KNOW THEY'LL COME BACK
FOR HER.

22:14.499 --> 22:15.801
- NO, THEY WON'T.

22:15.867 --> 22:18.303
'CAUSE I WISH
FOR A PLANET OF MOMS.

22:21.406 --> 22:22.407
[dads sobbing]

22:22.474 --> 22:23.408
YAY!

22:23.475 --> 22:26.745
[dads celebrating]

22:26.812 --> 22:29.915
- LADIES, WE'RE GOING TO NEED
A LOT OF FERNS.

22:32.217 --> 22:34.052
- WELL, THERE'S NO WAY
THIS COULD POSSIBLY

22:34.119 --> 22:35.520
COME BACK TO HAUNT YOU.

22:35.587 --> 22:37.155
[burgers sizzling]

22:41.293 --> 22:43.261
- PEOPLE OF DIMMSDALE,

22:43.328 --> 22:45.630
WE'VE COME
FOR YOUR KITTENS!

22:45.697 --> 22:47.599
- QUICK, DAD!
FLIP THE BURGERS!

22:49.000 --> 22:51.336
- [screams]

22:51.403 --> 22:53.405
OH, NEVER MIND.
